@startuml 1B_User_Registration
title 1-B · Fan Account Registration (UC-F01)

start
|Anonymous Visitor|
:Open the tenant fansite sign-up page;
:Enter email, username, password,\npassword confirmation and display name;

|System|
:Resolve tenant from domain / X-Tenant-ID;
if (Tenant is ACTIVE?) then (No)
  :Return 403 or maintenance page;
  stop
else (Yes)
  :Validate registration fields;
endif

if (Email or username already used in this tenant?) then (Yes)
  :Return 422 and prompt visitor to log in;
  stop
else (No)
  if (Password meets policy?) then (No)
    :Return password validation message;
    stop
  else (Yes)
    :Hash password;
    :Create Fan record scoped to tenant;
    :Issue bearer token for Free fan;
    :Send verification email if enabled;
  endif
endif

|Registered Fan (Free)|
:Open verification email if required;
:Access fan profile page;
:Can like, comment, RSVP,\nmanage addresses and buy merch;
stop
@enduml
